@baseUrl = http://localhost:7331

### List all orders (auto HTTP span from OTel middleware)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders

### Get order by ID — creates a manual child span (OrderStore.FindByID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/order-1

### Get non-existent order — child span records the error
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/order-999

### Create a new order — manual child span (OrderStore.Save) with attributes
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product": "OTel Coffee Mug",
  "qty": 3
}

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
